      {
        "order": 3,
        "text": "Add beef cubes and stir to coat with the spice paste. Cook until beef is browned on all sides."
      },
      {
        "order": 4,
        "text": "Add lemongrass, galangal, cinnamon stick, cloves, cardamom pods, and kaffir lime leaves. Stir well."
      },
