        "text": "Pour in coconut milk and add palm sugar and salt. Bring to a gentle simmer."
      },
      {
        "order": 6,
        "text": "Reduce heat to low and cook uncovered for about 3 hours, stirring occasionally and adding water if it gets too dry, until beef is tender and sauce is thick."
